trans-unit.source: Represents an attribute that specifies the name of a Microsoft Office Outlook message class to associate with the form region.
trans-unit.target: 表示一个属性，该属性指定要与表单区域相关联的 Microsoft Office Outlook 消息类的名称。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionMessageClassAttribute> class specifies the message class names of Outlook items that display the form region.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionMessageClassAttribute>类指定的显示窗体区域的 Outlook 项的邮件类名称。

trans-unit.source: When you add an **Outlook Form Region** item to an Outlook project, the wizard applies attributes to the form region factory class.
trans-unit.target: 当你将添加**Outlook 窗体区域**项向 Outlook 项目，该向导将特性应用于窗体区域工厂类。

trans-unit.source: You can also apply these attributes to the form region factory class manually.
trans-unit.target: 你还可以将这些特性手动应用到窗体区域工厂类。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Associating a Form Region with an Outlook Message Class](/visualstudio/vsto/associating-a-form-region-with-an-outlook-message-class.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[将窗体区域与 Outlook 邮件类关联](/visualstudio/vsto/associating-a-form-region-with-an-outlook-message-class.md)。

trans-unit.source: The name of a message class.
trans-unit.target: 消息类的名称。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionMessageClassAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionMessageClassAttribute" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="messageClass" /> argument is <see langword="null" /> or is empty.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="messageClass" /> 参数为 <see langword="null" /> 或为空。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="messageClass" /> argument is greater than 255 characters in length.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="messageClass" /> 参数的长度超过 255 个字符。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="messageClass" /> argument is invalid.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="messageClass" /> 参数无效。

trans-unit.source: For more information about valid message class names, see [Associating a Form Region with an Outlook Message Class](/visualstudio/vsto/associating-a-form-region-with-an-outlook-message-class.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关无效消息类名的详细信息，请参阅[将表单区域与 Outlook 消息类相关联](/visualstudio/vsto/associating-a-form-region-with-an-outlook-message-class.md)。
